%style
  :sass
    .section
      :padding-bottom 10px
      :border-bottom
        :width 1px
        :style dotted
        :color #FFF
      :margin-bottom 10px
      :padding-left 10px
      .blurb,.contents
        :text-indent 10px
      
#users_guide.help.dialog.modal
  #heading
    %h1 Prospektor&nbsp;User's&nbsp;Guide
  #toc.section
    %h2 Table of Contents
    .subsection
      .contents
        -[:introduction, :dashboard, :calling].each do |sec|
          =link_to sec.to_s.titleize, "##{sec.to_s}"
          .clear
  #introduction.section
    %a{ :name => 'introduction' }
    %h2 Introduction
    .blurb
      Prospektor&trade; is a prospect management system custom-built exclusively for Trigon Solutions.  This document is intended to provide |
      the user with a brief overview of its features and how to use them.
    .subsection
      .heading
        %h3 Confidentiality Notice
      .contents
        Before proceeding, understand that all information related to the Prospektor application and any of the data contained therein is |
        proprietary and confidential, and, as such, may not be revealed in any substantive manner to outside interests or competitors.  |
        Any such violation can be considered a breach of confidentiality of a trade secret and may be pursued as such.
  #dashboard.section
    %a{ :name => 'dashboard' }
    %h2 Dashboard
    .blurb
    .subsection
      .heading
      .contents
  #calling.section
    %a{ :name => 'calling' }
    %h2 Lead
    .blurb
    .subsection
      .heading
      .contents